DEBUG:openai._base_client:Request options: {'method': 'post', 'url': '/embeddings', 'files': None, 'post_parser': <function Embeddings.create.<locals>.parser at 0x12d69b700>, 'json_data': {'input': ['For my academic studies though, my school is definitely\u202c\n\u202dmore traditional in the classroom and has a heavy emphasis on industry topics that are more\u202c\n\u202dreliable than exciting, such as Java, OOP, and C development. While these fundamentals are\u202c\n\u202dimportant, I find myself constantly seeking to bridge the gap between traditional coursework and\u202c\n\u202dcutting-edge innovation.\u202c\n\u202dRecord a 90 second video and share why you believe you are a fit to be a GDSC Lead\u202c\n\u202dat your education institution. In the video, you are welcome to tell us about yourself and share\u202c\n\u202dyour interests and aspirations for the GDSC community at your educational institution. (publish\u202c\n\u202dvideo on youtube, have to make it a regular video and not YouTube Shorts)\u202c\n\u202dSummarize application (skillsets + past contribution + how you can contribute to gdsc at your\u202c\n\u202dcampus) also keep lighting good and create script and stuff\u202c\n\u202d1) if gdsc why do you want to be a gdsc lead\u202c\n\u202d2) leadership skills / past experience\u202c\n\u202d3) experience w/ technologies\u202c\n\u202dHello, my name is Will Gunter and I am a student at NC State. Ever since I was young,\u202c\n\u202dtechnology has been a big part of my life.'], 'model': 'text-embedding-3-small', 'encoding_format': 'base64'}}
