DEBUG:openai._base_client:Request options: {'method': 'post', 'url': '/embeddings', 'files': None, 'post_parser': <function Embeddings.create.<locals>.parser at 0x12d69f700>, 'json_data': {'input': ['Whether it was video games or <idk?> I have always\u202c\n\u202dloved the process of learning and mastering a skill-set, technology, or programming language.\u202c\n\u202dAnd I think this is why I am such a huge proponent of project based learning. The idea that you\u202c\n\u202dcan take a tool, language, or technology, no matter how small, and apply it in a way that gives\u202c\n\u202dmaximal leverage is something I’ve always found intriguing. <> I want to be a GDSC Lead\u202c\n\u202dbecause I want to spread my passion for technology to other people at my school and ignite the\u202c\n\u202dsame curiosity that I have to solve huge problems. I want to use this club as a platform to\u202c\n\u202dencourage creating solutions for problems that members have, and facilitate an environment\u202c\n\u202dwhere members will cultivate and spread ideas. Ideas that result not just in simple resume\u202c\n\u202dprojects, but in entrepreneurial opportunities which transform lives.'], 'model': 'text-embedding-3-small', 'encoding_format': 'base64'}}
