INFO:root:{'id': 'chatcmpl-B5tVnq2i8nbpS3uo2735BTUHrMozl', 'object': 'chat.completion', 'created': 1740744727, 'model': 'gpt-4o-mini-2024-07-18', 'choices': [{'index': 0, 'message': {'role': 'assistant', 'content': None, 'function_call': {'name': 'generate_library_room', 'arguments': '{"lessons":[{"factoids":[{"factoid_text":"The **GDG** (Google Developer Groups) is a community of developers who share their knowledge and experiences. They organize events, workshops, and talks to help each other grow.","question":{"type":"one_word_answer","text":"What does GDG stand for?","correct_choice":["Google Developer Groups"]}},{"factoid_text":"GDGs are *not* just for experienced developers; they welcome beginners and anyone interested in technology.","question":{"type":"multiple_choice","text":"Who can join GDGs?","correct_choice":["Anyone interested in technology"],"wrong_choices":["Only experienced developers","Only students","Only professionals"]}},{"factoid_text":"Each GDG chapter is unique, often focusing on local technologies and needs, making them *not* identical across the globe.","question":{"type":"fill_in_the_blank","text":"Each GDG chapter is unique, focusing on local __________ and needs.","correct_choice":["technologies"],"wrong_choices":["people","events","languages"]}},{"factoid_text":"GDGs often collaborate with Google to host events, which can include **hackathons**, coding sessions, and tech talks.","question":{"type":"one_word_answer","text":"What type of event is commonly hosted by GDGs?","correct_choice":["hackathons"]}},{"factoid_text":"Being part of a GDG can enhance your **networking** opportunities, connecting you with like-minded individuals and industry professionals.","question":{"type":"multiple_choice","text":"What is a benefit of joining a GDG?","correct_choice":["Networking opportunities"],"wrong_choices":["Guaranteed job offers","Free software licenses","Access to exclusive Google products"]}},{"factoid_text":"GDGs encourage members to share their projects and ideas, fostering a culture of *collaboration* and support.","question":{"type":"fill_in_the_blank","text":"GDGs encourage members to share their projects and ideas, fostering a culture of __________.","correct_choice":["collaboration"],"wrong_choices":["competition","isolation","indifference"]}},{"factoid_text":"Events are often free or low-cost, making them accessible to a wide audience, which is a key principle of GDGs.","question":{"type":"one_word_answer","text":"What is a common cost characteristic of GDG events?","correct_choice":["free"]}},{"factoid_text":"GDGs are *not* limited to just one programming language; they cover a variety of topics including web development, mobile apps, and cloud computing.","question":{"type":"multiple_choice","text":"What topics do GDGs cover?","correct_choice":["Web development, mobile apps, and cloud computing"],"wrong_choices":["Only web development","Only mobile apps","Only cloud computing"]}},{"factoid_text":"Joining a GDG can lead to personal growth, as members often learn new skills and technologies through hands-on experiences.","question":{"type":"fill_in_the_blank","text":"Joining a GDG can lead to personal __________.","correct_choice":["growth"],"wrong_choices":["decline","stagnation","confusion"]}}]},{"factoids":[{"factoid_text":"GDGs often host **meetups** where members can discuss the latest trends in technology and share their experiences.","question":{"type":"one_word_answer","text":"What type of gathering do GDGs often host?","correct_choice":["meetups"]}},{"factoid_text":"These meetups are *not* just lectures; they often include interactive sessions where participants can engage and ask questions.","question":{"type":"multiple_choice","text":"What is a feature of GDG meetups?","correct_choice":["Interactive sessions"],"wrong_choices":["Only lectures","No questions allowed","Strictly formal"]}},{"factoid_text":"GDGs can help you stay updated with the latest **Google technologies**, which are constantly evolving.","question":{"type":"fill_in_the_blank","text":"GDGs help you stay updated with the latest __________ technologies.","correct_choice":["Google"],"wrong_choices":["Microsoft","Apple","Amazon"]}},{"factoid_text":"Many GDGs also focus on **diversity** and inclusion, encouraging underrepresented groups to participate in tech.","question":{"type":"one_word_answer","text":"What aspect do many GDGs focus on to encourage participation?","correct_choice":["diversity"]}},{"factoid_text":"GDGs are *not* just about learning; they also provide opportunities for members to showcase their skills through presentations and workshops.","question":{"type":"multiple_choice","text":"What do GDGs provide opportunities for?","correct_choice":["Showcasing skills"],"wrong_choices":["Avoiding presentations","Only attending workshops","No skill development"]}},{"factoid_text":"Members can gain **mentorship** from experienced developers, which can be invaluable for career growth.","question":{"type":"fill_in_the_blank","text":"Members can gain __________ from experienced developers.","correct_choice":["mentorship"],"wrong_choices":["competition","isolation","confusion"]}},{"factoid_text":"GDGs often use social media to promote their events and connect with members, making it easier to stay informed.","question":{"type":"one_word_answer","text":"What platform do GDGs often use to promote events?","correct_choice":["social media"]}},{"factoid_text":"Participating in GDG events can lead to **job opportunities**, as many companies look for talent in these communities.","question":{"type":"multiple_choice","text":"What can participating in GDG events lead to?","correct_choice":["Job opportunities"],"wrong_choices":["Less networking","No career growth","Limited skill development"]}},{"factoid_text":"GDGs are a great way to meet **mentors** and peers who can guide you in your tech journey.","question":{"type":"fill_in_the_blank","text":"GDGs are a great way to meet __________ and peers.","correct_choice":["mentors"],"wrong_choices":["competitors","strangers","detractors"]}}]},{"factoids":[{"factoid_text":"The **GDG** community is global, with chapters in many countries, allowing for a rich exchange of ideas and cultures.","question":{"type":"one_word_answer","text":"What type of community is GDG?","correct_choice":["global"]}},{"factoid_text":"GDGs are *not* just about coding; they also cover topics like design, project management, and entrepreneurship.","question":{"type":"multiple_choice","text":"What topics do GDGs cover besides coding?","correct_choice":["Design, project management, and entrepreneurship"],"wrong_choices":["Only coding","Only design","Only project management"]}},{"factoid_text":"Many GDGs host **workshops** where participants can learn hands-on skills in a collaborative environment.","question":{"type":"fill_in_the_blank","text":"Many GDGs host __________ where participants can learn hands-on skills.","correct_choice":["workshops"],"wrong_choices":["lectures","seminars","webinars"]}},{"factoid_text":"GDGs often encourage members to contribute to **open source** projects, promoting collaboration and learning.","question":{"type":"one_word_answer","text":"What type of projects do GDGs encourage members to contribute to?","correct_choice":["open source"]}},{"factoid_text":"Networking at GDG events can lead to lifelong friendships and professional connections, which are *not* to be underestimated.","question":{"type":"multiple_choice","text":"What can networking at GDG events lead to?","correct_choice":["Lifelong friendships and professional connections"],"wrong_choices":["Only acquaintances","No connections","Temporary friendships"]}},{"factoid_text":"GDGs often feature guest speakers from the tech industry, providing insights into real-world applications of technology.","question":{"type":"fill_in_the_blank","text":"GDGs often feature guest speakers from the __________ industry.","correct_choice":["tech"],"wrong_choices":["fashion","food","sports"]}},{"factoid_text":"Being part of a GDG can help you develop a **portfolio** of projects, showcasing your skills to potential employers.","question":{"type":"one_word_answer","text":"What can being part of a GDG help you develop?","correct_choice":["portfolio"]}},{"factoid_text":"GDGs are *not* just for individual learning; they also promote team projects, enhancing collaboration skills.","question":{"type":"multiple_choice","text":"What do GDGs promote besides individual learning?","correct_choice":["Team projects"],"wrong_choices":["Solo projects","Independent study","No collaboration"]}},{"factoid_text":"Joining a GDG can be a stepping stone to a successful career in technology, opening doors to various opportunities.","question":{"type":"fill_in_the_blank","text":"Joining a GDG can be a __________ to a successful career in technology.","correct_choice":["stepping stone"],"wrong_choices":["barrier","hindrance","detour"]}}]}]}'}, 'refusal': None}, 'logprobs': None, 'finish_reason': 'stop'}], 'usage': {'prompt_tokens': 1190, 'completion_tokens': 1805, 'total_tokens': 2995, 'prompt_tokens_details': {'cached_tokens': 0, 'audio_tokens': 0}, 'completion_tokens_details': {'reasoning_tokens': 0, 'audio_tokens': 0, 'accepted_prediction_tokens': 0, 'rejected_prediction_tokens': 0}}, 'service_tier': 'default', 'system_fingerprint': 'fp_06737a9306'}
