DEBUG:openai._base_client:Request options: {'method': 'post', 'url': '/embeddings', 'files': None, 'post_parser': <function Embeddings.create.<locals>.parser at 0x1089b1790>, 'json_data': {'input': ['Yet as I soon found out,\u202c\n\u202das a Senior Patrol Leader - the head youth leader of the troop - that is not my main\u202c\n\u202dresponsibility. These tasks are by no means unimportant, but I had five other members of my\u202c\n\u202dsenior staff who were specifically assigned to these roles. From this experience, and many like\u202c\n\u202dit, I soon found out that my main responsibility as a leader is to drive the engine of the\u202c\n\u202dorganization (the troop) to accomplish its grander vision, which in this case was leaving for the\u202c\n\u202dcampout. I have always prided myself on my independence, but it was around this time that I\u202c\n\u202dlearned to leverage the specialization of the other roles (my friends) so I can focus my attention\u202c\n\u202don any blockers we had and guide the troop towards our broader goals.'], 'model': 'text-embedding-3-small', 'encoding_format': 'base64'}}
