DEBUG:openai._base_client:Request options: {'method': 'post', 'url': '/embeddings', 'files': None, 'post_parser': <function Embeddings.create.<locals>.parser at 0x108a19310>, 'json_data': {'input': ['Evident from my past\u202c\n\u202dexperience with technologies and my leadership roles in Boy Scouts, I believe that I would be a\u202c\n\u202dgreat fit to be a GDSC lead for my campus.\u202c\n\u202dDiagnostic Test:\u202c\n\u202dobjective test to access your personality\u202c\n\u202dno need to study, it is based on experience\u202c\n\u202dCannot reschedule ( 30 - 60 minutes)\u202c\n\u202dis an Eliminatory phase\u202c\n\u202dInterview Round:\u202c\n\u202d30-minute 1:1 G-meet\u202c\n\u202dTest of technical skills + logical thinking\u202c\n\u202dPlans for community growth and stuff\u202c\n\u202dEverything about you\u202c\n\u202dIntroduce yourself, DSA based questions, projects, not the emphasis tho\u202c\n\u202dEvent based questions (if so and so happens, how would you deal with it?)\u202c\n\u202dDo not be stressed, very nice interviewers I think - want to understand you + your capabilities\u202c\n\u202dDo not be scared\u202c\n\u202dpreference to final or pre-final year students and to students who have been involved in their\u202c\n\u202dcampuses GSDC club (we don’t have one tho???)\u202c\n\u202dCan organize LOTS of events\u202c'], 'model': 'text-embedding-3-small', 'encoding_format': 'base64'}}
