INFO:root:{'id': 'chatcmpl-B5uElR2VafTeO8khXFGCZAxWW4txM', 'object': 'chat.completion', 'created': 1740747515, 'model': 'gpt-4o-mini-2024-07-18', 'choices': [{'index': 0, 'message': {'role': 'assistant', 'content': None, 'function_call': {'name': 'generate_library_room', 'arguments': '{"lessons":[{"factoids":[{"factoid_text":"The **GDG** (Google Developer Groups) is a community-driven initiative that connects developers to share knowledge and collaborate on projects. It encourages networking and learning through events and meetups.","question":{"type":"one_word_answer","text":"What does GDG stand for?","correct_choice":["Google Developer Groups"]}},{"factoid_text":"GDGs are found in many countries around the world, making it a global community. This allows developers from different backgrounds to come together and learn from each other.","question":{"type":"multiple_choice","text":"What is a key feature of GDGs?","correct_choice":["Global community"],"wrong_choices":["Local only","Online only","No events"]}},{"factoid_text":"Members of GDGs often participate in workshops, hackathons, and talks led by experienced developers. This hands-on approach helps to solidify learning.","question":{"type":"fill_in_the_blank","text":"GDG members participate in workshops, hackathons, and ___ led by experienced developers.","correct_choice":["talks"],"wrong_choices":["meetings","conferences","seminars"]}},{"factoid_text":"One of the main goals of GDGs is to foster **innovation** and creativity among developers. This is achieved through collaboration and sharing of ideas.","question":{"type":"one_word_answer","text":"What is one of the main goals of GDGs?","correct_choice":["innovation"]}},{"factoid_text":"GDGs often focus on specific technologies, such as **Android**, **Web Development**, or **Cloud Computing**. This specialization allows for deeper learning.","question":{"type":"multiple_choice","text":"What do GDGs often focus on?","correct_choice":["Specific technologies"],"wro