INFO:root:{'id': 'chatcmpl-B5uEnNoQawLsrzkB8qrAP3D2JULwT', 'object': 'chat.completion', 'created': 1740747517, 'model': 'gpt-4o-mini-2024-07-18', 'choices': [{'index': 0, 'message': {'role': 'assistant', 'content': None, 'function_call': {'name': 'generate_library_room', 'arguments': '{"lessons":[{"factoids":[{"factoid_text":"**Python** is known for its simplicity and readability, making it a great choice for beginners. It uses indentation to define code blocks instead of braces or keywords.","question":{"type":"multiple_choice","text":"What is a key feature of **Python** that makes it beginner-friendly?","correct_choice":["Simplicity and readability"],"wrong_choices":["Complex syntax","Requires advanced knowledge","Uses braces for code blocks"]}},{"factoid_text":"**JavaScript** is primarily used for web development, allowing developers to create interactive websites. It runs in the browser, making it essential for front-end development.","question":{"type":"fill_in_the_blank","text":"**JavaScript** is mainly used for __________ development.","correct_choice":["web"],"wrong_choices":["desktop","mobile","game"]}},{"factoid_text":"**Java** is an object-oriented programming language that is designed to be platform-independent. This means that code written in **Java** can run on any device that has the Java Virtual Machine (JVM).","question":{"type":"one_word_answer","text":"What does JVM stand for?","correct_choice":["Java Virtual Machine"]}},{"factoid_text":"**C++** is an extension of the **C** programming language and includes features like classes and objects. It is widely used in game development and high-performance applications.","question":{"type":"multiple_choice","text":"What is a primary use of **C++**?","correct_choice":["Game development"],"wrong_choices":["Web development","Data analysis","Mobile apps"]}},{"factoid_text":"**Ruby** is known for its elegant syntax that is easy to read and write. It is often used in web development, particularly with the Ruby on Rails framework.","question":{"type":"fill_in_the_blank","text":"**Ruby** is often associated with __________ development.","correct_choice":["web"],"wrong_choices":["system","game","mobile"]}},{"factoid_text":"**PHP** is a server-side scripting language designed for web development. It is embedded in HTML and is widely used for creating dynamic web pages.","question":{"type":"one_word_answer","text":"What does PHP stand for?","correct_choice":["PHP: Hypertext Preprocessor"]}},{"factoid_text":"**Swift** is a programming language developed by Apple for iOS and macOS applications. It is designed to be fast and efficient, with a focus on safety and performance.","question":{"type":"multiple_choice","text":"What platform is **Swift** primarily used for?","correct_choice":["iOS and macOS"],"wrong_choices":["Windows","Linux","Android"]}},{"factoid_text":"**Go**, also known as Golang, is a statically typed language developed by Google. It is known for its simplicity and efficiency, particularly in cloud services and server-side applications.","question":{"type":"fill_in_the_blank","text":"**Go** is often used in __________ services.","correct_choice":["cloud"],"wrong_choices":["desktop","mobile","game"]}},{"factoid_text":"**Kotlin** is a modern programming language that is fully interoperable with **Java**. It is officially supported for Android app development and is known for its concise syntax.","question":{"type":"one_word_answer","text":"What type of applications is **Kotlin** primarily used for?","correct_choice":["Android"]}}]},"lessons\':[{"\n\n'}, 'refusal': None}, 'logprobs': None, 'finish_reason': 'length'}], 'usage': {'prompt_tokens': 1188, 'completion_tokens': 697, 'total_tokens': 1885, 'prompt_tokens_details': {'cached_tokens': 0, 'audio_tokens': 0}, 'completion_tokens_details': {'reasoning_tokens': 0, 'audio_tokens': 0, 'accepted_prediction_tokens': 0, 'rejected_prediction_tokens': 0}}, 'service_tier': 'default', 'system_fingerprint': 'fp_06737a9306'}
